---
import Shield from './Shield.astro';
---
<section class="relative bg-brand-primary text-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -left-20 -bottom-16 text-white/[0.04]" aria-hidden="true"><Shield class="w-[420px] h-[500px]" /></div>
  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 sm:px-8 py-24 md:py-32 grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_400px] gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
   <div>
    <p class="reveal flex items-center gap-2 font-heading font-medium text-[11px] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-brand-accent mb-5">
      <Shield class="w-3.5 h-4" /> Local Knowledge
    </p>
    <h2 class="reveal font-heading font-extrabold tracking-[-0.025em] leading-[1.08] text-[clamp(2rem,4.5vw,3rem)] max-w-3xl">What Happy Valley homes need from their plumber</h2>
    <div class="reveal mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-5 text-white/75 text-[1.0625rem] font-light leading-relaxed">
      <p>Happy Valley grew quickly through the 1970s and 80s, and a lot of that housing stock is now hitting the age where original plumbing starts to show its years. Vitrified clay drainage pipes — standard back then — crack and let tree roots in, which is why blocked and collapsed drains are one of the most common calls we get in the area.</p>
      <p>The other recurring issue is hot water. Electric and early gas storage units installed a couple of decades ago are well past their service life, and the foothills location means cold mornings expose a failing element fast. We carry common replacement units so most Happy Valley homes are back to hot water the same day.</p>
      <p>Older homes here also tend to run on galvanised steel supply pipes that corrode and restrict flow, and slab-era construction means hidden leaks can track under the floor before anyone notices a damp patch. Our acoustic leak detection finds them without tearing up the house.</p>
      <p>We've spent a decade working on exactly these homes across the southern suburbs, so we know what's behind the walls before we open them. That's how we can quote a fixed price upfront and stand behind the work with a Lifetime Labour Warranty.</p>
    </div>
   </div>
   <div class="reveal">
     <img src="/images/hero-tradesman.jpg" alt="Licensed local tradesperson in work gear" class="w-full h-full max-h-[460px] object-cover rounded-xl shadow-[0_30px_70px_-25px_rgba(0,0,0,0.6)] ring-1 ring-white/10" />
   </div>
  </div>
</section>
